dct_description_sm: California with a double indentation along the northern coast without any place names.
Dedicated to Jacobo Dno. Compton, Honmi. Comitis Northamptoniae, with coat of arms between the two hemispheres.
Issued with similar world map (Entry #1010), which shows the ancient world with the eastern hemisphere continents named.

Issued in: Geographia Emendata & Locupletata, / Dionysius Periegetes, 1688. Reissued in 1704, 1718 (Editio tertia), 1726 (Editio quarta, with Typis Guil. Bowyer), and 1738 (Editio quinta, with Typis T. Wood).
